parameters: .........Hayato, wake up.... This is the original world. *sniffle*

.....Seria... thank you for saving me. You really are a \c[14]hero\c,
aren't you.
\F[24]\AA[F]What on earth are you two up to...
\F[20]\AA[F]Oh, you protected me? I knew it, I love you so much♡

\F[18]\AA[F]If you make any more moves on my Hayato, it's a
different story. I'll cut you!

\F[24]\AA[F]Alright, alright. I give up. \c[14]There's no way I
can win against the sacred sword holder and the cute bodyguard.

\F[23]\AA[F]But... \c[14]the news that a real hero is in Variente
\cwill spread, won't it?
\F[17]\AA[F]No, that's bad. If that happens... this place...
Merill... please. Can't you do something about it?

\c[27]I'll do \canything... I don't want to see the innocent
people of Variente get hurt!
\F[23]\AA[F]Fine. This time, for Hayato's sake, I'll keep quiet.

\F[24]\AA[F]And... even though I had absolutely no intention of
letting anyone out from the church basement, it was brilliantly
breached... out of respect.
\F[1]\AA[F]Somehow... there seems to be a hidden agenda...

\F[24]\AA[F]What's the difference? Once Lady Sadi's severe
treatment is over, the information will be shared anyway.
\F[23]\AA[F]Goodbye, little girl. See you again, Hayato♡
For now... I wonder if it was good.
\F[10]\AA[F]We need to think of a countermeasure, don't we....
That's right. But I'll keep trying to protect it from now on.

\F\c[14]\AA[F]I am, after all, \c[14]descended from a person who
was called a hero in the olden times\c.

It seems so, since you were able to activate the \c[14]Holy
Sword\c.
In the end, who is the real descendant of the \c[14]Goddess\c?

.........I don't know. At least it's not me, and they might be somewhere
in the world\c.
If Sadi revives, we'll start the search again....

\F[1]\AA[F]We can't just sit around. We need to take action
quickly!

We have to prepare to go search for the
\F\c\AA[F]\c[14]Goddess\c!

\F\c[14]\AA[F]Even though I'm a complete amateur in combat, this
\c[14]Holy Sword\c had an amazing power. I'm sure I can protect
us!

\F[8]\AA[F]I don't want to end up in a situation like some erotic
doujinshi, so we'll go after proper training!
....You really are brave, Seria. I want to follow you too!
By the way, Seria, what was the thing you forgot at the church?
O-oh! Seria, Hayato, you've come back!!
\F[1]\AA[F]I will never forgive you, you know.

I'm sorry! I got carried away with Merill just because I was
lustful...♡

\F[8]\AA[F](I think it would be better if you quit being a
clergyman.)

\F[10]\AA[F](But he's been a pervert from the start, so I can't
really hate him...)
Ah... now that you mention it, what was it.... Seria.
This was lying around. Take it before you forget.
\F[3]\AA[F]Ah... Thank you! I've been looking for this!

I see... Make sure not to forget something filled with your
feelings.
Alright, I think I'll write a love letter to Merill too!
\F[1]\AA[F]I wish it could be burned along with the letter.
Well then, shall we have fun with Merill today as well?
................It's really, truly, a sight I haven't seen in a long time.
Thank you, Miss Seria. Ann won't make a mistake anymore.
